{
  "id": "69bff9daa5452df2a733cccd",
  "title": "2026/03/22 みじっこマイク",
  "created": 1774189020,
  "updated": 1774801934,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bff9daa5452df2a733cccd",
      "text": "2026/03/22 みじっこマイク",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189020,
      "updated": 1774189020
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9df000000000060234f",
      "text": "[2026/03/22]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189023,
      "updated": 1774189027
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9df0000000000602350",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189023,
      "updated": 1774189023
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9dc000000000060234d",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189020,
      "updated": 1774189021
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9e30000000000602351",
      "text": "\t[卓上マイク]を探している",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189028,
      "updated": 1774189035
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9ea0000000000602352",
      "text": "\t[Shure]のマイク良さそう？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189035,
      "updated": 1774189074
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9fb0000000000602353",
      "text": "\t\t[SM7B]、[SM7dB]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189052,
      "updated": 1774189074
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffa0d0000000000602354",
      "text": "\t\t\t高すぎ（7～8万）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189069,
      "updated": 1774189087
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffa160000000000602355",
      "text": "\t\t\tしかもこれ単体で動かなくてオーディオインターフェースかミキサー必須",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189078,
      "updated": 1774189105
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffcd1000000000060236c",
      "text": "\t\t\tめちゃくちゃ感度が低い為アンプ必須",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189778,
      "updated": 1774189797
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffce5000000000060236d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[SM7dB]のみアンプも内蔵されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189798,
      "updated": 1774189823
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffa310000000000602356",
      "text": "\t\t[MV7]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189106,
      "updated": 1774189117
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffa420000000000602357",
      "text": "\t\t\t5万弱ぐらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189123,
      "updated": 1774189284
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffae40000000000602358",
      "text": "\t\t\tUSBでそのまま接続可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189284,
      "updated": 1774189288
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffba10000000000602361",
      "text": "\t\t\t[MV7とSM7B：どちらのマイクを選ぶべきか？2つのマイクの違いは？ - Shure 日本 https://www.shure.com/ja-JP/insights/mv7-or-sm7b-which-mic-is-right-for-you]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189474,
      "updated": 1774189474
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffae80000000000602359",
      "text": "\t\t[MV7+]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189288,
      "updated": 1774189292
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffaec000000000060235a",
      "text": "\t\t\tMV7より高音質になったらしい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189292,
      "updated": 1774189299
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffaf3000000000060235b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[配信・実況・ナレーションに最適な神マイクSHUREのMV7＋登場！MV7との違いを交えてポイントをご紹介！！｜島村楽器 名古屋パルコ店 https://www.shimamura.co.jp/shop/nagoya/article/product/20240409/22092]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189299,
      "updated": 1774189305
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffafa000000000060235c",
      "text": "\t\t\tUSB端子はmicroBからType-Cへ変更",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189307,
      "updated": 1774189339
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffb38000000000060235d",
      "text": "\t\t[SM58]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189368,
      "updated": 1774189371
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffb3c000000000060235e",
      "text": "\t\t\t1.5万～2万",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189372,
      "updated": 1774189379
    },
    {
      "id": "69c953e50000000000099b78",
      "text": " \t\t\t[XLR]接続のみ対応なので[オーディオインターフェース]分追加課金が必要",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774801893,
      "updated": 1774801899
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffb45000000000060235f",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ボーカルマイク]なので音が印象強め",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189381,
      "updated": 1774189401
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffb5f0000000000602360",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tなので配信や通話には向かなさそう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189408,
      "updated": 1774189415
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffbad0000000000602362",
      "text": "\t[ダイナミックマイク]と[コンデンサーマイク]の違いも調べておかなければ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189486,
      "updated": 1774189507
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffbf50000000000602365",
      "text": "\t\t[ダイナミックマイクとコンデンサーマイクの使い分けを、オーディオテクニカおすすめモデルを使って解説。 - Always Listening by Audio-Technica（オーディオテクニカ） https://www.audio-technica.co.jp/always-listening/articles/usage-microphone/]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189558,
      "updated": 1774189558
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc510000000000602366",
      "text": "\t\t[ダイナミックマイク]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189649,
      "updated": 1774189656
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc5d0000000000602368",
      "text": "\t\t\t感度が低い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189662,
      "updated": 1774189665
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc7c000000000060236a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t雑音が入りにくい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189692,
      "updated": 1774189708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc8b000000000060236b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t近くで話さないと音が入りづらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189708,
      "updated": 1774189743
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc580000000000602367",
      "text": "\t\t[コンデンサーマイク]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189657,
      "updated": 1774189660
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffc610000000000602369",
      "text": "\t\t\t感度が高い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189666,
      "updated": 1774189668
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffd59000000000060236e",
      "text": "\t\t\tより繊細な音も入りやすい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189914,
      "updated": 1774189931
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffd6a0000000000602370",
      "text": "\t\t\t雑音が多い環境には向かない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189931,
      "updated": 1774189958
    },
    {
      "id": "69bffd870000000000602371",
      "text": "\t\t\tスタジオ向き",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189960,
      "updated": 1774189962
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8893700000000009eb902",
      "text": "\t[VRChat]でも使うマイクと考えると卓上では少し難があるかもしれない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750007,
      "updated": 1774750034
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8895200000000009eb903",
      "text": "\t\tまあこれは必要であれば別に買うのが良さそう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750034,
      "updated": 1774750051
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8896400000000009eb904",
      "text": "\t\t[ピンマイク]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750053,
      "updated": 1774750069
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8897c00000000009eb906",
      "text": "\t\t\t身につけるタイプのマイクがあれば音声入りやすいかも",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750076,
      "updated": 1774750099
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8897600000000009eb905",
      "text": "\t\t[Mutalk]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750070,
      "updated": 1774750075
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8899300000000009eb907",
      "text": "\t\t\t身につけるタイプのマイク過激版",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750100,
      "updated": 1774750120
    },
    {
      "id": "69c953bf0000000000099b74",
      "text": "\t結局[SM58]か[MV7+]かのどちらかで悩んでいる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774801856,
      "updated": 1774801873
    },
    {
      "id": "69c953d10000000000099b75",
      "text": "\t\tMV7+はUSB接続できるって強みがある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774801873,
      "updated": 1774801934
    },
    {
      "id": "69bff9dd000000000060234e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774189021,
      "updated": 1774189021
    },
    {
      "id": "69c891c300000000006a0416",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752195,
      "updated": 1774752196
    },
    {
      "id": "69c891c400000000006a0418",
      "text": "\tコンデンサーマイクはダイナミックマイクより繊細な扱いが必要、という点は押さえておくと良いかも？",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752197,
      "updated": 1774752225
    },
    {
      "id": "69c891e200000000006a0419",
      "text": "\t\tダイナミックマイクは雑に扱ってもそんなに壊れませんが、コンデンサーマイクは場合によっては壊れます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752226,
      "updated": 1774752251
    },
    {
      "id": "69c891fb00000000006a041a",
      "text": "\t\t\t特に室温と湿気に気を使わないとダメな場面もあるので、そこは注意が必要かもです",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752251,
      "updated": 1774753013
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8920f00000000006a041b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t↑はコンデンサーマイクの話です",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752271,
      "updated": 1774752306
    },
    {
      "id": "69c894c400000000006a042a",
      "text": "\t\t\t恐らく耐久度としては",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752965,
      "updated": 1774752974
    },
    {
      "id": "69c894cf00000000006a042c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tダイナミックマイク  > コンデンサーマイク",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752976,
      "updated": 1774752989
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c9360000000000be4ac4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tなるほど、耐久度的にもダイナミックマイクが優っているんですね…[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774766391,
      "updated": 1774766406
    },
    {
      "id": "69c894dd00000000006a042d",
      "text": "\t\t\tになるんじゃないかと",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752990,
      "updated": 1774752995
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8922e00000000006a041d",
      "text": "\tVRChat のマイクの場合、有線ピンマイクより無線の小型マイクの方がいいかも？しれません",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752303,
      "updated": 1774753003
    },
    {
      "id": "69c892b700000000006a0420",
      "text": "\t\tマイクとしての取り回しとしては無線マイクの方が楽な場面があります",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752440,
      "updated": 1774752780
    },
    {
      "id": "69c892c800000000006a0421",
      "text": "\t\t\t無線マイクの場合、PCと接続できればそれでいいので、そこは楽です",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752456,
      "updated": 1774752780
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8934900000000006a0426",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[nyarla.icon]の場合 [DJI Mic mini] を [Pico 4 Ultra] にマスキングテープでくっつけてます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752585,
      "updated": 1774752780
    },
    {
      "id": "69c893a600000000006a0427",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[DJI Mic mini] の場合マイクが磁石でくっつく + 磁石が付属しているので、 磁石の方をヘッドセットに貼り付けて、その上でマイクの方を付けてます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752678,
      "updated": 1774752780
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c94e0000000000be4ac5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t確かに無線の選択肢は盲点でした[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774766414,
      "updated": 1774766423
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c9570000000000be4ac6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t普段買わない（有線派）なので…",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774766423,
      "updated": 1774766433
    },
    {
      "id": "69c892fd00000000006a0423",
      "text": "\t\t有線ピンマイクの場合、物によっては音圧が出ない、という問題もあります",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752510,
      "updated": 1774752809
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8931d00000000006a0424",
      "text": "\t\t\tハードウェア的に増幅できればいいんですが、そうでない場合ソフトウェア的にやる必要があります",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752541,
      "updated": 1774752780
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8941400000000006a0428",
      "text": "\t\t\tヘッドセット本体と有線ピンマイクを直接接続する場合、音量調整ができないと場合によっては詰みます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752789,
      "updated": 1774753058
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8944700000000006a0429",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[nyarla.icon]はそれで一回詰んだことがあるので、そこは注意が必要かな、と感じてます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752839,
      "updated": 1774752924
    },
    {
      "id": "69c891c400000000006a0417",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774752196,
      "updated": 1774752196
    }
  ]
}